.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: azalea, balloon-flower, tulip, aconite, dahlia
There are 5 different nationalities: english, spanish, ukranian, norwegian, japanese
House: townhouse, gothic-revival, art-deco, craftsman, wooden
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, tea, milk, orange-juice, water
The people have 5 different jobs:  analyst, firefighter, lawyer, teacher, bartender

1. the english is the person who growsazalea
2. the spanish is the analyst
3. the person drinking coffee is the person who growsballoon-flower
4. the ukranian is the person drinking tea
5. the person who growsballoon-flower is to the right of the person who growstulip
6. the townhouse house is the bartender
7. the gothic-revival house is the person who growsaconite
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the firefighter
11. the gothic-revival house is to the left or right of the teacher
12. the craftsman house is the person drinking orange-juice
13. the japanese is the wooden house
14. the norwegian is to the left or right of the person who growsdahlia

.:: Answer ::.
